name: Capture One Session File
summary: Learn about .COSESSIONDB files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: COSESSIONDB files are located in "Sessions" folders in the Capture One directory on your computer. COSESSIONDB files replaced .COL, COL 60, COL50, and COL45 files, which were used by older versions of Capture One. These older files can still be opened by Capture One.

description: A COSESSIONDB file is a session file created by Capture One, a program used for managing digital photos. It stores a collection of photos that have been selected by the user and organized as an album. COSESSIONDB files are used to organize your work as a project.
